---
import Container from './Container.astro';
---
<section class="border-y border-rule bg-paper">
  <Container class="pt-[30px] pb-5 text-center">
    <p
      class="mx-auto max-w-[60ch] text-balance font-display text-[clamp(24px,2.4vw,34px)] font-normal leading-[1.3] tracking-[-0.01em]"
    >
      Black-box and white-box evaluations give complementary <br> viewpoints on agents'
      plans, goals and failures. <br> Both are needed for auditing frontier AI agents.
    </p>
    <a
      href="/about.html"
      class="mt-7 inline-block border-b border-gold pb-0.5 text-xs tracking-[0.04em] text-gold-deep"
    >
      MORE ABOUT US →
    </a>
  </Container>
</section>
